        How to Terminate Your Real Estate Agent's Authority in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        If you have lost confidence in your agent, here is how the Form 6 exclusive authority works in Queensland, and what your options actually are before and after the exclusive period ends.
      </p>
